title: Labor To Restore Fair Compensation For Crash Victims (Premier of Victoria)
text: ( Source : Premier of Victoria ) The Andrews Labor Government will fulfil another election commitment by reversing legislation introduced by the previous Liberal Government that restricted Victorians ' ability to claim common law compensation
